web.translations.welcomes_contributors_f.en: welcomes contributors for both existing and new languages.
web.translations.welcomes_contributors_f.translation: pozdravlja sodelavce za obstoječe in nove jezike.

web.translations.whove_helped_with_trans.en: who've helped with translations as we continue to develop new features.
web.translations.whove_helped_with_trans.translation: ki so pomagali pri prevodih, medtem ko nadaljujemo z razvojem novih funkcij.

web.translations.as_we_add_new_features_.en: As we add new features, our translations gradually need updates to stay current. This affects both onetimesecret.com and thousands of self-hosted installations worldwide.
web.translations.as_we_add_new_features_.translation: Ko dodajamo nove funkcije, naši prevodi postopoma potrebujejo posodobitve, da ostanejo aktualni. To vpliva tako na onetimesecret.com kot na tisoče samo-gostovanih namestitev po vsem svetu.

web.translations.remember_to_include_you.en: - remember to include your email if you're not logged in. Every translation helps more people communicate securely.
web.translations.remember_to_include_you.translation: - ne pozabite vključiti svoje e-pošte, če niste prijavljeni. Vsak prevod pomaga več ljudem varno komunicirati.

web.translations.start_a_new_translation.en: Start a new translation from our

web.translations.update_a_language_direc.en: Update a language directly through our GitHub project
web.translations.update_a_language_direc.translation: Posodobite jezik neposredno preko našega projekta GitHub

web.translations.review_existing_transla.en: Review existing translations using the language selector above
web.translations.review_existing_transla.translation: Preglejte obstoječe prevode z uporabo izbirnika jezika zgoraj

web.translations.ready_to_help_some_ways.en: Ready to help? Some ways to contribute:
web.translations.ready_to_help_some_ways.translation: Pripravljeni pomagati? Nekateri načini za prispevanje:

web.translations.the_following_people_ha.en: The following people have donated their time to help expand the reach of Onetime Secret:
web.translations.the_following_people_ha.translation: Naslednje osebe so darovale svoj čas, da bi pomagale razširiti doseg Onetime Secret:

web.translations.fork_on_github_and_subm.en: Fork on GitHub and Submit a PR
web.translations.fork_on_github_and_subm.translation: Razdvojite na GitHub in pošljite PR

web.translations.your_language_skills_ca.en: Your language skills can help expand access to secure communication.
web.translations.your_language_skills_ca.translation: Vaše jezikovne spretnosti lahko pomagajo razširiti dostop do varne komunikacije.

web.translations.thanks_to_our_community.en: Thanks to our community, we support over 20 languages today. However, with our rapid development pace, many translations need updates to stay current. This affects both onetimesecret.com and the thousands of self-hosted installations worldwide.
web.translations.thanks_to_our_community.translation: Zahvaljujoč naši skupnosti danes podpiramo več kot 20 jezikov. Vendar zaradi našega hitrega tempa razvoja mnogi prevodi potrebujejo posodobitve, da ostanejo aktualni. To vpliva tako na onetimesecret.com kot na tisoče samo-gostovanih namestitev po vsem svetu.

web.translations.since_2012_onetime_secr.en: Since 2012, Onetime Secret has provided a secure way to share sensitive information worldwide. With users across regions where English isn't the primary language, accurate translations are essential for making secure communication accessible to everyone.
web.translations.since_2012_onetime_secr.translation: Od leta 2012 Onetime Secret zagotavlja varen način deljenja občutljivih informacij po vsem svetu. Z uporabniki v regijah, kjer angleščina ni primarni jezik, so natančni prevodi bistvenega pomena za dostopnost varne komunikacije vsakomur.
